            <p>Area to be abandoned DEPARTMENT FOR INFRASTRUCTUREMap No. IN1/19/562240 referred to in “The Back Street at Duncairn Gardens, Belfast (Abandonment) Order (Northern Ireland) 2020” made by the Department on 18th August 2020 and coming into operation on 7th October 2020.<b>© Based upon the Ordnance Survey map with the Permission of the Director and the Chief Executive.</b>Crown Copyright         SCALE 1:500</p>
